text: Timo Bernd Hübers (born 20 July 1996) is a German professional footballer. He plays as a defender for Hannover 96. On 11 March 2020, during the 2019–20 coronavirus pandemic, Hübers tested positive for COVID-19. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:German footballers Category:Sportspeople from Lower Saxony Category:1.
